    <bcl:section id="d2e27">
      <bcl:marginalnote>Prescribed class of employees</bcl:marginalnote>
      <bcl:num>2</bcl:num>
      <bcl:text>For the purposes of the definition of "employee" in section 1 of the <in:doc>Public Interest Disclosure Act</in:doc>, members of government bodies designated in the Schedule who exercise an adjudicative function of a tribunal are prescribed.</bcl:text>
